      <title>卡塔尔在最新的阿萨德后提升中向叙利亚提供叙利亚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/qatar-supplies-syria-with-natural-gas-in-latest-post-assad-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡塔尔开始通过前总统巴沙尔·阿萨德（Bashar al-Assad）倒塌后，通过约旦向叙利亚提供天然气，这是饱受战争war国家临时政府的最新提升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/qatar-supplies-syria-with-natural-gas-in-latest-post-assad-boost</guid>
